title: TOA PAYOH STREET CAT FOUND BRUTALLY MUTILATED, EYES & FUR PLUCKED OUT
text:
TOA PAYOH STREET CAT FOUND BRUTALLY MUTILATED, EYES & FUR PLUCKED OUT   Advertisement 
Dear All Singapore Stuff, 
At Toa Payoh Lorong 2 Blk 144. One of our favourite Toa Payoh street cats, which we saw grown from a kitten, was found dead with grievous mutilation. Its fur and eyes were plucked out and its body was dumped in the bushes. This is a sad day.. 
What kind of sick fuck gets his thrills from torturing and killing street cats?! 
CatLuver A.S.S. Contributor
